{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "0c92b1a9-9f2f-4026-8277-65938771222f", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/0c92b1a9-9f2f-4026-8277-65938771222f@1.pkg/1772597593477/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597594588", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/0c92b1a9-9f2f-4026-8277-65938771222f@1.pkg/1772597593477/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597594588"}, "identifier": "0c92b1a9-9f2f-4026-8277-65938771222f", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>这道题考查的是对科技发展与社会关系的辩证思考。我们来分析各个选项：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>A项（用户体验）：虽然指出了老年人使用困难的问题，但仅关注\"用户体验\"这个单一维度，忽略了题干中提到的环保问题。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>B项（统筹社会效益与环境保护）：完整涵盖了题干中的两个关键点：老年人接受度低（社会效益）</span><span>、</span><span>待机能耗问题（环境保护）</span><span>，</span><span>体现了全面协调的发展观。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>C项（现代化标志）：将技术普及简单等同于现代化，是片面观点，且未回应题干中的问题。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>D项（无条件推广）：\"无条件\"的说法绝对化，违背了可持续发展的原则。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>正确答案：B．技术发展需要统筹社会效益与环境保护</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（原创）随着5G和物联网技术的普及，2025年我国智能家居渗透率已达65%。某研究团队发现：老年人对智能家电的接受度仅38%，主要因操作复杂；而环保组织则担忧智能设备的全天候待机模式会增加能耗。这启示我们（　）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（原创）随着5G和物联网技术的普及，2025年我国智能家居渗透率已达65%。某研究团队发现：老年人对智能家电的接受度仅38%，主要因操作复杂；而环保组织则担忧智能设备的全天候待机模式会增加能耗。这启示我们（　）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/0c92b1a9-9f2f-4026-8277-65938771222f@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754626261312", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>科技创新必须坚持以人为本，提升用户体验</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>技术发展需要统筹社会效益与环境保护</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>智能产品普及程度是现代化的重要标志</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>创新成果应当无条件推广以促进技术迭代</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（原创）随着5G和物联网技术的普及，2025年我国智能家居渗透率已达65%。某研究团队发现：老年人对智能家电的接受度仅38%，主要因操作复杂；而环保组织则担忧智能设备的全天候待机模式会增加能耗。这启示我们（　）</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet